1614	[(conj-0) $\mathrm{pullbackComp}^{-1}$ is the $\operatorname{leftAdjointCompIso}$ of $\mathrm{pushforwardComp}$]
1615	  \label{lem:pullbackComp_inv_eq_leftAdjointCompIso_inv}
